  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.8.8">
<l>tuḷaiyār karumeṉ kuḻalāyc ciyartan tukilvā riyuṅciṟ ṟilcitait tumuṟṟā</l>
<l>viḷaiyār viḷaiyāṭ ṭoṭukā talveḷḷam viḷaivit tavammā ṉiṭamvēl neṭuṅkaṇ</l>
<l>muḷaivā ḷeyiṟṟu maṭavār payiṟṟu moḻikēṭ ṭiruntu mutirā taviṉcol</l>
<l>vaḷaivā yakiḷḷai maṟaipā ṭunāṅkūr maṇimā ṭa<supplied>k</supplied>kōyil vaṇaṅkeṉ maṉaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My heart, worship at Maṇimāṭa Temple in Nānkūr where curved-beaked parrots</l>
<l rend="indent">	sing the Vedas in immature, sweet prattle,</l>
<l>Having heard the practice words of simple girls with long lance[-like] eyes</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] bright, budding teeth,</l>
<l>The place of the lord who, having snatched the clothes of the milkmaids</l>
<l rend="indent">with dark hair, soft [and] full of curls,</l>
<l>And ruined their little [sand] huts with this play,</l>
<l rend="indent">raised in those immature young ones a flood of love.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
